      "body": "From the thread, \"the torrent will be updated once every few months, when the checkpoints are updated\" suggests a relationship but I wasn't sure exactly what to read into that.  Wasn't hassling you about the torrent; I raise the issue just because micha mentioned on IRC that just by noticing it was a bit overdue, he ended up inserting the previous checkpoint, leading me to think it's not something people remember to do very often.\n",
